title: How to Change Your Thoughts
itunes:title: How to Change Your Thoughts
description:
Can I be honest with you? It is not your thoughts that are the issues in your life, it is what you are thinking about your thoughts... aka if you are identifying yourself with those thoughts. Curious what I am talking about? Check out this episode to learn more about how to are not your thoughts, you are just the observer.
